content: awesome
Please fix... The last couple of days it hasn't been working for Google app, Google news, poweramp and YouTube when it was working perfectly fine
replyContent:
Hello
When apps get updated from playstore, if you are getting force closes while trying to open them follow the steps below:

1. Uninstall app overlay
2. Restart your phone
3. Install app overlay
4. Restart your phone
5. Enable app overlay

If you are using Synergy, just swipe the updated overlays to delete then add them back and rebuild the theme

content: No longer workings with Google app, Google News, YouTube music and powerapm. Please fix.
replyContent:
Hello
When apps get updated from playstore, if you are getting force closes while trying to open them follow the steps below:

1. Uninstall app overlay
2. Restart your phone
3. Install app overlay
4. Restart your phone
5. Enable app overlay

If you are using Synergy, just swipe the updated overlays to delete then add them back and rebuild the theme

replyContent:
It themes it just fine without any issues at all. Make sure you choose OxygenOS10 from the top of the overlay list and not just Android 10. Also select dark theme from system settings and set the accent to default.

Cheers
